## Generate C tags with function prototypes and local variables
ctags --C-kinds=+pl *

## Nearly everything for ctags
## see ctags --list-kinds=c
## -R for recursive
ctags-exuberant --C-kinds=+defglmpstuvx *

### Vim
## Go to Tag
C-]

## Return to previous file postion
C-t

## Open Tag in new split
C-w C-]
